Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:12.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 9th Month (September 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencil sharpeners!\NPencil sharpeners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,Okajima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencil sharpeners!\NPencil sharpeners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pencil sharpeners!\NPencil sharpeners!\NPencil sharpeners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{Shaving sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's better than using normal one to shave.\NElectricity is cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah….
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{Shaving sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:25.39,Song,,0,0,0,,"The waves slurp\NSeparate it."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:32.13,Note,,0,0,0,,{Shaving sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:32.13,Song,,0,0,0,,"Sweet and snug the clouds"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:41.84,Song,,0,0,0,,"Where is Gourd Island going?\NWhere is it taking us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think a pencil is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not use the electric pencil sharpener anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:05.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,2nd year of the Reiwa era, 9th month (September 2020)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!\NHaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, is this a pencil sharpener?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how nostalgic!\NThat's right! A pencil sharpener.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:38.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{Shaving sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:42.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{Shaving sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Grandma's too\NMizuki's mother also used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NIs it that old?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki!\NDon't carry your own luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:29.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,Only Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!\NAh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I used a hint of grandfather's secret sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, can I eat it every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when my grandpa is discharged from the hospital\NYou can eat something even more delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't the taste a bit strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tongue is numb because your eating while drinking milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been drinking milk with my meals for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going to stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has mom drunk milk with dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NShe has been like this since she was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Been like this...\NFirst of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mom who kept insisting, 'Drink milk, drink milk,' to the point of being annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to drink a lot of milk and grow up big. It's a pure parent's love, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown too much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For Showa-era moms\NI want you to reflect on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many people like me, who grew tall and have complex feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a lie that drinking milk will make you grow taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?\NSo it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm!\NSee, this is also very flavorful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki... Is your mom's cooking always mild in flavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know because it's always just microwaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NDon't rely on microwaves, make it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dad heard that, he would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been busy lately, so we've had a lot of microwave meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you're not busy, we still have a lot of microwave meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Microwave, microwave, microwave. Stop saying 'microwave' over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, no matter how busy you are, make dinner at least twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it even if you don't tell me. See? I even made dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.\NWhat you made is moving-in soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Soba is just boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Soba, at least, isn't a microwave meal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki's school play?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard they might not do it this year because of COVID, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the sports day got canceled too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, they decided to hold the school play, just on a smaller scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mizuki, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I only have a small part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do! You can't have that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you have to treasure every single moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Living on stage is what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was on stage, that was what mattered the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As an actress, that's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandma, you weren't an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 9th Month (September 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NYou're doing Kobutori Jii-san for the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What role are you playing, Taeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An old woman? Oh, a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Village Child 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just village child 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do have lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she has the most lines among the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NWhat's about a crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(Clears throat)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home. First one... { I am just taking from the 1991 anime subs for this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home. \NFirst one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:55.08,Top,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home. \NFirst one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you had the most lines, but it's just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The village scene is only the one part Taeko just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't really have much to do with the story of Kobutori Jii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home. \NFirst one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:19.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,Josai Ward Municipal Koshin Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then I'll start with Yamada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Looking out) Ah, it's another good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try doing it a little more energetically.\NGood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does it say when we come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Appear while playing."\NWhat are we going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...\NHmm... anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good!\NLet's think about it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what about hopscotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's hopscotch or something\NYou can come out right away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okajima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When people are practicing let's look on quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,First one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one line, but that girl keeps on.\NHow much practice is enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.49,Top,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're practicing at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.47,Top,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.42,Top,,0,0,0,,First one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all they did the the first half today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't even able to practice up to her scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.82,Top,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.61,Top,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.30,Top,,0,0,0,,First one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I've started to feel sorry for my younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.61,Top,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.48,Top,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!\NBehold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Three birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Four birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.58,Top,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Mr. Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Mr. Okajima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only say the lines written in the script, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back now..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.35,Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up… Yamada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bump on your cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,brings happiness to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance, dance have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Only say the lines written in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone say it louder this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I couldn't hear the lines today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez she was just too enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she only had one line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides no one is even watching the villager scenes anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said thanks to that, they understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "understood"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They figured out how to approach their role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I see….
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{No clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:53.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Grateful Crane\NFifth Grade, Class Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:12:00.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,Story of Kobutori Jii-san ("Grandpa with a Lump")\NFifth Grade, Class Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, Class 5's "Grandpa with a Lump".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I'm getting nervous..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She only has one line anyway..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Ahh, what a wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… Dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So… Well then I shall
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go… to the mountain… and… set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha… Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa… Pa… Please take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Waa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.24,Top,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the crows fly home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.93,Top,,0,0,0,,She pointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Two birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Three birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Four birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She waved her hand….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-chan was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What children's theater group is she in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's that good will she be an actress in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but really, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the direction for the role.... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Natsuki doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing fine, but work seems tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, since early spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her salary went down, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the workload increased," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Things should get a bit easier for her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,since she's moving into our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll save on rent too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She have anyone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be dating someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think she's considering remarriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki is there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see….
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, speaking of which—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki's school
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to hold the school play as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mizuki is in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it! So, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her some acting tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki must have been so annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I say so myself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For a fifth-grade girl, I had
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,genius-level acting techniques. Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I've heard it a million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... If only Dad hadn't said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely would've become a great actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have surpassed Keiko Matsuzaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,don't underestimate Keiko Matsuzaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a huge actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha! You're right. Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Natsuki and the others moved in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, having the sound of people's footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in the house is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And somehow it makes me reminisce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was Mizuki's age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I had so many happy memories
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Taeko…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, do what makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I've been thinking lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 40, I suddenly said I wanted to open a Western-style restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and quit my job….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we live close by,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely got to see my grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you can make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Working non-stop from morning till night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, Taeko,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the life ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to find
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,new joys and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,please take care of your own health.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:25.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,Second Life for the Senior Generation\NLet's find goals, dreams, and things we like.{    第二の人生 (Dai-ni no Jinsei) - This translates to "Second Life" and is a general heading for the section.\N    Below that, there's a smaller headline: シニア世代のセカンドライフ (Shinia Sedai no Sekando Raifu) - This means "Second Life of the Senior Generation."\N    To the right of the main image of the woman, there's a prominent headline: 「目標や夢、好きなことを見つけよう」 (Mokuhyou ya Yume, Suki na Koto wo Mitsukeyou) - This translates to "'Let's find goals, dreams, and things we like.'"\N    Above the picture of the woman on the right, it says: 湯川 恵子 さん (Yukawa Keiko-san) - This identifies the person in the article as Keiko Yukawa.\N    Below her name, there's another headline: 79歳で世界新記録 (79-sai de Sekai Shin-kiroku) - This means "(She set) a new world record at 79 years old."\N\NTherefore, the main topics highlighted on this page are about the "second life" of senior citizens, featuring the story of Keiko Yukawa who achieved a new world record in marathon running at the age of 79, and encouraging readers to find goals, dreams, and things they enjoy in their lives.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A new life…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:36.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,Second Life for the Senior Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:40.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,Josai Ward Municipal Koshin Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“This is Mark Smith.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mark Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mark Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mark Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mark Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it! Pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey what are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey let's go….
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is starting. Hurry up, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close….
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada-kun, change your clothes like a man, confidently
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be embarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy! It's P.E. P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go on a business trip Saturday, October 17th?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes….
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,10:00 Mizuki School Arts Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Chief, about that day….
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,19:21 - Thank you! Sorry.\NArrived at the station. What should we eat?\N19:43 I'll arrive in 2 minutes. I feel like having meat today\NWant to get food today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to make dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I make for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Natsuki-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're going to live with Taeko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, word travels fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san is really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's excited to live with her grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And are you excited, Natsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always nagging me about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet and sour pork?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.90,Top,,0,0,0,,Finishing touch… There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you adding pineapple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It's standard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes the meat tender and adds sweetness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know I hate pineapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just pick it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hate pineapple,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I love sweet and sour pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! You're such a troublesome kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mirror's in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:27.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 12th month (December 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week is my birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Toko-chan, I'll bring pineapple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pineapple?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I told Dad when I was invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,D- D-Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihoko-chan used to live in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,people call their father by their first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's like calling him Taeko or Yaeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know in America they eat pineapples.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Raw?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just bananas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pineapples, real ones. Not canned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Daddy's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Taeko, you're still up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here bananas for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Welcome back Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Kenzo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,buy a pineapple tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She learned something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, pineapple!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Not canned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.30,Top,,0,0,0,,A real pineapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that kind of thing isn't sold in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,The next day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad where did you buy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At a Ginza department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it must've been expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko the Knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:08.82,Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we cut this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful when cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Wow! It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.19,Top,,0,0,0,,Taeko, let me smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit sour smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom too Mom too…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:56.84,Top,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes different from canned ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to Taeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.40,0:24:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.61,0:24:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko, you don't have to force yourself to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.87,0:24:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.76,0:24:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.16,0:24:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.61,0:24:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:25:04.07,Song,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, I've been asked out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.07,0:25:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.27,0:25:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But….
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.07,0:25:07.08,Song,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.15,0:25:10.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Is it still too soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:13.82,Song,,0,0,0,,Feels happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.39,0:25:17.03,Song,,0,0,0,,but also a bit scary
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.18,0:25:18.40,Song,,0,0,0,,Beating heart, beating heart
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.26,0:25:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit Dad sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.23,0:25:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.01,0:25:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Dad's health?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.77,0:25:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know he's been saying some weak-hearted things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.92,0:25:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"From now on do what makes you happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.95,0:25:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the life ahead I hope you find
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.47,0:25:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,new joys and pleasures", he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Dad reflecting in his own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop was so busy he probably feels he troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never once thought of it as trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.23,0:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly glad I married your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is this bragging?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.22,0:26:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In my life those words would never come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.71,0:26:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're a single mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom could you stop twisting the knife so hard in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.25,0:26:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For my life ahead…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.93,0:26:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once COVID settles down, how about taking a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Hokkaido, where Aunt Yaeko lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.77,0:26:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. You should go visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd probably find it a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why are you coming all the way from Tokyo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.51,0:26:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day Nana-neechan told me the same thing on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.94,0:26:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband is really uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.62,0:26:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go on a solo hot spring trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.89,0:27:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.14,0:27:10.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,Second Life{第二の人生 (Dai ni no jinsei)\N\NThis phrase means "second life" in Japanese. It often refers to a significant change in one's life, such as a career change after retirement, starting a new chapter after a major event, or pursuing a long-held dream later in life.}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.56,0:27:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A solo hot spring trip would just be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.20,0:27:18.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,<Lots of results for what to do as a retiree>{ Therefore, the gist of what you are looking at is a list of search results related to the concept of a "second life", likely in the context of retirement, new beginnings, or significant life changes.\N\NThe snippets below each search result provide brief summaries of the content found on those pages, all revolving around the theme of a "second life." You can see topics like:\N\N    Enjoying a second life after retirement (with mentions of courses for men in Ehime and Ibaraki prefectures).\N    Discussions about the anxieties and realities of a second life after retirement.\N    Planning for a second life after turning 60.\N    Opportunities for seniors, such as a theater audition, as part of their second life.\N    Financial considerations and challenges in the context of a second life.}
