Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.84,0:27:36.64,Sign,,0,0,0,,\N○ The performance that was canceled in spring will now be be performed this autumn!\N○ Shakespeare for those 60 years old and over!!! Actors wanted!! Beginners welcome!!!\N○ Up-and-coming director, Shinnosuke Sakaguchi, challenges the "possibilities of an elderly theater company"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.06,0:27:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.26,0:27:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.90,0:27:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.15,0:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Taeko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.27,0:27:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.37,0:27:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.80,0:28:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning I got into a fight with my dumb son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.27,0:28:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He just won't study at all, so I told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.21,0:28:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“Enough already! I'm throwing away all your games!”, and then he said
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,“Go ahead. I'll just buy them again with my New Year's money next year.”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.92,0:28:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.70,0:28:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously I just want to smack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids have their own strengths and weaknesses, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.53,0:28:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take math for me, I was so terrible at it I hated studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.06,0:28:31.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 9th Month (September 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Um… You see… Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.45,0:28:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Before this test, um… we had art class.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, um.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.10,0:28:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we did blow painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.50,0:28:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.94,0:28:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.53,0:28:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… we dripped paint onto paper, and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.27,0:28:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then blew on it to make patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.41,0:29:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A- And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.91,0:29:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My head… started hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.05,0:29:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.94,0:29:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I blew so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.56,0:29:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you got this score?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.62,0:29:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- Yeah… that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.00,0:29:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this is such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.90,0:29:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you at least know the correct answers for the ones you got wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.46,0:29:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.11,0:29:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.81,0:29:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.49,0:29:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this!? What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.94,0:29:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Please explain it to her. She doesn't seem to get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.73,0:30:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? But, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.11,0:30:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, how could this happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.10,0:30:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Taeko? Are you feeling okay in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.40,0:30:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said, you would explain it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If she did it normally, there's no way she'd get a score like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Taeko isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.42,0:30:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a headache from blow painting, right? Right, Taeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.16,0:30:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just flip the numerator and denominator and multiply, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they taught you at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.70,0:30:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.44,0:30:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dividing fractions by fractions… what does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.98,0:30:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.52,0:30:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.15,0:31:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dividing two-thirds of an apple by one-fourth means...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.09,0:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you divide two-thirds of an apple among four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.59,0:31:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How many apples per person?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.27,0:31:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, per person, simplifying two-twelfths
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.45,0:31:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,makes one-sixth of an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.98,0:31:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's multiplication!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.62,0:31:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if we're multiplying, why does the number get smaller?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.03,0:31:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too fixated on apples, that's why you don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.73,0:31:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For multiplication, keep the top and bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For division, flip them, that's all you need to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Taeko should get an IQ test. Wouldn't that be a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.80,0:31:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm… but when she entered school, they said she was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.27,0:31:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just got dumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.98,0:31:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When Taeko was a baby, she fell from the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.45,0:31:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! In a baby walker!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.25,0:32:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I thought she was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.09,0:32:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's catching up now…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.92,0:32:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.10,0:32:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you divide two-thirds of an apple
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.37,0:32:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,by one-fourth…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.60,0:32:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you divide two-thirds among four people,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.43,0:32:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,how much does each person get?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.39,0:32:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.42,0:32:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't get it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That whole math concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.62,0:32:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what was your childhood dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.43,0:32:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.97,0:32:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.79,0:32:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just curious what a girl who was so bad at math dreamed of becoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.21,0:32:59.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,Basic Information
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.84,0:33:07.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,Self-Promotion / Personal Appeal: "Ever since my elementary school days, when I experienced acting in a school play, I've longed to stand on the stage again someday. I've turned 64 this year, my children are settled, and my husband tells me to do what I like. I would like to give it my all. I will do my best."\N\NHandling of Personal Information: <boilerplate legalese> \N\NAgreement and Submission
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.58,0:33:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.20,0:33:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.75,0:33:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.19,0:33:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too embarrassing now… Ugh…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.76,0:33:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.53,0:33:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
