Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.68,0:33:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.74,0:33:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent it....
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.60,0:33:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I sent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.53,0:33:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.78,0:33:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.96,0:33:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.21,0:33:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.81,0:33:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.58,0:33:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.01,0:33:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No no... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.01,0:33:38.47,Top,,0,0,0,,Grandma!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.00,0:33:40.38,Top,,0,0,0,,Grandma, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.28,0:33:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.39,0:33:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.62,0:33:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma you really wanted to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.72,0:33:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandma's father said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.92,0:33:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.64,0:33:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then it was different from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.30,0:34:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Women got married and staying at home was considered happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.74,0:34:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.97,0:34:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of person was Grandma's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.63,0:34:22.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 5th Month (May 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.26,0:34:25.59,Top,,0,0,0,,The House of Representatives on the 14th… The Japan Socialist Party….
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.13,0:34:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.93,0:34:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Dad is way too soft on you, Taeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.77,0:34:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we supposed to only get dolls on birthdays or for Christmas!?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.11,0:34:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that so, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.19,0:34:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.59,0:34:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Ta-bo?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.98,0:34:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, big sis Yaeko got a furisode even though it wasn't her coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.12,0:34:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then it wasn't for her ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.26,0:34:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, we don't get lots of little things bought for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.29,0:34:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, we get something big once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.03,0:34:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.16,0:35:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.90,0:35:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That furisode will eventually belong to Taeko, so it's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ever get is hand-me-downs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.57,0:35:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kids can't even get hand-me-downs, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.99,0:35:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry up and give me that enamel bag already!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.17,0:35:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I haven't given it to you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.92,0:35:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give something so childish to Taeko already.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.47,0:35:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A secondhand handbag…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.61,0:35:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it….
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.90,0:35:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then I won't give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.79,0:36:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.69,0:36:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.06,0:36:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this kind of bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.90,0:36:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Taeko, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.94,0:36:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.24,0:36:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a handbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.75,0:36:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Yae-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.08,0:36:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,lend her that enamel bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.59,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.53,0:36:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch….
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.94,0:36:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.78,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.71,0:36:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.21,0:36:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.12,0:37:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-bo's not going? {Had Tarbo originally, switching it to Ta-bo like used above at dinner}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.02,0:37:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.56,0:37:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.73,0:37:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.77,0:37:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of rain}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.92,0:37:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.59,0:37:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Barefoot…!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.40,0:37:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.27,0:38:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Crying sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.49,0:38:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.35,0:38:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.56,0:38:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Running out barefoot was a shameful and disgraceful act that made him angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.90,0:38:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're selfish, a father wants them to grow up beautifully. {was わがままでもいいから\N美しく育ってほしいって。"Even if you're selfish, I want you to grow up beautifully." seems like something the father is thinking}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.07,0:38:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's just Grandma's guess though.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to see your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.76,0:38:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.84,0:38:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,have you ever wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.60,0:38:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.27,0:38:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.14,0:39:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.89,0:39:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey why don't you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.15,0:39:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.23,0:39:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it come to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.56,0:39:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.78,0:39:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.07,0:39:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.24,0:39:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Shunsuke….
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no intention to marry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.91,0:39:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.49,0:39:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.11,0:39:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just for fun then stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.84,0:40:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I have a child doesn't mean I'm not thinking about remarriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.13,0:40:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking that someday it'll happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah….
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:22.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,Nenrinza Company Inaugural Performance\NAudition Venue\NWaiting Room {劇団 年輪 座 旗揚げ 公演\NGekidan Nenrinza Hataage Kōen\NTroupe Nenrinza Inaugural Performance\N\Nオーディション 会場\NŌdishon Kaijō\NAudition Venue\N\N受付・控室\NUketsuke・Hikaeshitsu\NReception・Waiting Room}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a hospital waiting room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.52,0:40:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.09,0:40:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nice to meet you I'm Kida.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.44,0:40:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sugimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.98,0:40:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.14,0:40:48.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.18,0:40:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Next person please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.95,0:40:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katsuya Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sachiyo Mizumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.34,0:40:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.66,0:41:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Taeko Sugimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.63,0:41:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hiroki Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.81,0:41:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.57,0:41:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.39,0:41:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does feel like a hospital….
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.93,0:41:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.78,0:41:23.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,(Whiteboard) Nenrinza Company\NInaugural Performance: "A Midsummer Night's Dream"\NAudition\NScheduled Performance Dates: Saturday, October 22nd{劇団 年輪 座\NGekidan Nenrinza\NTroupe Nenrinza\N\N旗揚げ公演 「夏の夜の夢」\NHataage Kōen "Natsu no Yo no Yume"\NInaugural Performance "A Midsummer Night's Dream"\N\Nオーディション\NŌdishon\NAudition\N\N公演予定日 10/22(土)～\NKōen Yoteibi 10/22 (Do) ~\NScheduled Performance Dates: Saturday, October 22nd ~}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.87,0:41:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The play we'll be performing this time is Shakespeare's, "A Midsummer Night's Dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.94,0:41:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a comedy centered around marriage between men and women, but I also see it as a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.28,0:41:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The story takes place in a forest near Athens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.12,0:41:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There, nobles, craftsmen, and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.13,0:41:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,fairies living in the forest appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.83,0:41:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then let's start reading the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.56,0:41:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Katsuya Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.97,0:41:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.51,0:41:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.02,0:41:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like there's no choice but to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.71,0:41:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.79,0:41:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Sugimoto Taeko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.15,0:41:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.54,0:41:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.12,0:42:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.86,0:42:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh I'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.39,0:42:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the saddest I've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.09,0:42:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.54,0:42:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The mist soaks me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.60,0:42:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The thorns scratch me…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.66,0:42:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't crawl or move forward anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.77,0:42:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just have to rest….
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this until dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.28,0:42:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.62,0:42:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yamada Hiroki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.26,0:42:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.94,0:42:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.60,0:42:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.79,0:42:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Phone Ringing}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.80,0:42:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sugimoto speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.70,0:42:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.37,0:42:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.86,0:42:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.14,0:42:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.98,0:43:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.31,0:43:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.50,0:43:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.86,0:43:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.78,0:43:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.50,0:43:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.63,0:43:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.40,0:43:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that about the audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.93,0:43:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.01,0:43:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow… Grandma did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.50,0:43:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.80,0:43:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.49,0:43:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.94,0:43:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.78,0:43:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.59,0:43:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.62,0:43:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma passed the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.88,0:43:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.54,0:43:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.69,0:43:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.12,0:43:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma is going to perform on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.79,0:43:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki is in the school play
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.92,0:43:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma is also in a play!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do our best in practice together!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.08,0:43:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.80,0:43:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.45,0:44:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.57,0:44:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.24,0:44:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Footsteps}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.63,0:44:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.18,0:44:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.13,0:44:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of the school play
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.67,0:44:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom might have to work….
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.54,0:44:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to watch it…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.61,0:44:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.60,0:44:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.94,0:44:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.81,0:44:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... I've finally gotten busy recently..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.71,0:44:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.95,0:44:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.19,0:44:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.39,0:45:03.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,List of the cast and characters for Shakespeare's "A Midsummer Night's Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.41,0:45:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to working with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.50,0:45:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.07,0:45:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah…}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.41,0:45:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.13,0:45:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Taeko Sugimoto, playing the role of Hermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.08,0:45:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… Please feel free to call me Taeko or Tae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.58,0:45:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give it my all
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.16,0:45:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid causing trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.79,0:45:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.21,0:45:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.85,0:45:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.35,0:45:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Suu suu suu… Suu shuus… Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.60,0:45:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,, "Duke Theseus."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.03,0:45:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thi… Theseus….
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.89,0:45:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke Theseus!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.41,0:45:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, Egeus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.34,0:45:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.28,0:45:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.80,0:45:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Egeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.55,0:45:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.91,0:45:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being called.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.20,0:46:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.75,0:46:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it… my line?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.34,0:46:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… Where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.31,0:46:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.84,0:46:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Umm…}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.10,0:46:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I have an important announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.90,0:46:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.69,0:46:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.71,0:46:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.27,0:46:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.24,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I must file a complaint against my own daughter, Hermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.86,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.91,0:46:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah….}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.25,0:46:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermia
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.10,0:46:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermia...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.00,0:46:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to react there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.92,0:46:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Um, for now Let's stick to what's written in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.92,0:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.21,0:46:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.47,0:46:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Egeus,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.49,0:46:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.13,0:46:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.71,0:46:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um...}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.73,0:46:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Step forward Demetrius.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.66,0:46:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.81,0:46:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait um Shibui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.41,0:46:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your role, Shibui-san is Lysander.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.22,0:46:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.77,0:46:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The one just called was Demetrius.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.60,0:46:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... oh that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.61,0:46:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right it's you, Kida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.37,0:46:51.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.23,0:46:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.94,0:46:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… this man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.10,0:46:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one I have consented to give my daughter to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.62,0:47:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Step forward Lysander.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.70,0:47:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.67,0:47:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the man who has secretly confused my daughter's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.06,0:47:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have sent love songs to my daughter and delivered tokens of your love, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.73,0:47:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Forgive me. I....
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.77,0:47:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of clapping}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.90,0:47:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.77,0:47:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.70,0:47:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Too fast Too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.62,0:47:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh....}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.29,0:47:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermia's line is still two pages ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.12,0:47:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.17,0:47:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't hold it in anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.02,0:47:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no please hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.40,0:47:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an order to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.25,0:47:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.49,0:47:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.44,0:47:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.95,0:47:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more okay? Let's stick to what is written in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.72,0:47:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... Okay! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.60,0:47:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alright.}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.91,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.10,0:47:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then uhm page four....
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.59,0:47:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Only say the lines that are written in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.41,0:48:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"You have sent love songs to my daughter" from there please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.11,0:48:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! This is so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hehehe}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.68,0:48:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at 10 years old, I was told the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.48,0:48:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't grown at all, it's actually pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.06,0:48:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rehearsals for a play move along so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.93,0:48:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if they do move fast, in the end, it's just a bunch of amateurs, so we can't do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.23,0:48:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rehearsals are progressing, but so is our forgetfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.20,0:48:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.07,0:48:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.91,0:48:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, in times like these,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.99,0:48:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to be able to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.78,0:48:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I embarrass myself, it helps me stay positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.75,0:48:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.26,0:48:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.76,0:48:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san, that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.55,0:48:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.77,0:49:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh!? Haha! Hehehe….}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.43,0:49:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 5th Month (May 1966)
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.71,0:49:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬～}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.05,0:49:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.98,0:49:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is there someone named Okajima here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.83,0:49:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.57,0:49:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hehehehe}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.82,0:49:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirota-kun from my class,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.24,0:49:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,said he likes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.92,0:49:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okajima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.24,0:49:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Kyaa~!}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.24,0:49:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh~?}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.91,0:49:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow….}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.06,0:49:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was surprising seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.45,0:49:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.10,0:49:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.28,0:49:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.52,0:49:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who is Hirota-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.39,0:49:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh he's from Class 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:49:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.92,0:50:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro! They're calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.60,0:50:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.10,0:50:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okajima-san from Class 5 said, "I don't know how to respond to something like that." {not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.41,0:50:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.33,0:50:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Okajima-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.47,0:50:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.73,0:50:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh… I didn't say anything though.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.28,0:50:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro you said you like that girl from Class 5, Okajima, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.79,0:50:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just told her for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.79,0:50:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.29,0:50:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What….
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.84,0:50:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Taeko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.30,0:50:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No running in the hallway. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.44,0:50:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Hirota-kun for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.81,0:50:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.49,0:50:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I properly told him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.82,0:50:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you Taeko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.32,0:50:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.59,0:50:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah….
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.32,0:51:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Hirota from Class 4 likes Okajima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.93,0:51:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirota is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.47,0:51:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.39,0:51:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to lose in the finals for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.76,0:51:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.97,0:51:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.63,0:51:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh the one after school this Saturday…?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.64,0:51:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That one you think you'll lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.33,0:51:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Hirota!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.48,0:51:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.65,0:51:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.52,0:51:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready… Rock-paper-scissors, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.36,0:51:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.56,0:51:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.62,0:51:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,five, four, three, two, one, zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.63,0:51:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now, the match between Class 5-4 and 5-5 begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.68,0:51:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.62,0:51:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.80,0:51:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.78,0:51:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.87,0:51:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Hi Ro Ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.81,0:51:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Hi Ro Ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.48,0:52:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Hi Ro Ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.21,0:52:00.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Okajima is watching you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.22,0:52:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Hi Ro Ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.55,0:52:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Hi Ro Ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.42,0:52:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.13,0:52:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause and cheers}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.40,0:52:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.44,0:52:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.77,0:52:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.18,0:52:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cheer for Class four, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.56,0:52:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no… I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.78,0:52:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Class Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.22,0:52:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Class Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.47,0:52:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go Class Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.42,0:52:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.79,0:52:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause and cheers}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.63,0:52:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah….
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.57,0:52:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬～}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.81,0:53:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Game set. Five to three. Class four wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.38,0:53:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.92,0:53:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cheers}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.09,0:53:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sue's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.85,0:53:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue's.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.95,0:53:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.99,0:53:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sue's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.53,0:53:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me? You guys don't even understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.52,0:53:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the rules of baseball at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.60,0:53:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher will treat everyone to ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.77,0:53:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cheers}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.30,0:53:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um….
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.21,0:54:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.65,0:54:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,cloudy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.30,0:54:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or sunny days…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.38,0:54:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.01,0:54:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.98,0:54:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudy….
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.40,0:54:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.27,0:55:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.77,0:55:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close….
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.24,0:55:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that was close... I almost ran into Sawada in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.33,0:55:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is still as creepy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.26,0:55:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.08,0:55:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'm so glad I didn't turn out like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.08,0:55:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you wasting your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.21,0:55:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you wasting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.32,0:55:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.41,0:55:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready….
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.01,0:55:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.62,0:55:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.79,0:55:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.62,0:55:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.29,0:55:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good Perfect Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.67,0:56:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.22,0:56:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm Alright next is…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.89,0:56:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san and Sawada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.43,0:56:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.57,0:56:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay okay okay okay okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.37,0:56:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada-kun! You're a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.86,0:56:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so stand up straight, stand tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.64,0:56:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.25,0:56:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look everyone's laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.75,0:56:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.92,0:56:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so you two umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.91,0:56:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hold hands and say the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.26,0:56:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Soft laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.76,0:56:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.51,0:56:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.10,0:56:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.98,0:56:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.77,0:56:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.55,0:56:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.78,0:56:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.27,0:56:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.41,0:56:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.26,0:56:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.08,0:56:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.59,0:57:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I heard your stage rehearsals have started?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.72,0:57:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really so fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.19,0:57:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, say something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.89,0:57:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Mom do whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.73,0:57:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never thought she'd become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.57,0:57:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.09,0:57:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A second life as an actress? Never heard of that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.73,0:57:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hahahahaha….}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.91,0:57:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've accepted this illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I die I'll have to live with it and deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.08,0:57:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want Mom to enjoy herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.07,0:57:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.44,0:57:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well fine
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.56,0:57:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She can do whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.72,0:57:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again being jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.89,0:57:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.26,0:57:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that Natsuki is trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.76,0:57:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not the only one who has it tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.10,0:57:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.14,0:57:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom has always done her job as your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.87,0:57:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I know….
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.14,0:57:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.22,0:58:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to be friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.09,0:58:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everyone finds me creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.93,0:58:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not forcing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.23,0:58:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think you're creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.90,0:58:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.43,0:58:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Used to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.77,0:58:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Being talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.48,0:58:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.00,0:58:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That… how should I put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.52,0:58:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like being a girl…? {not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.93,0:58:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.66,0:58:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate men.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.10,0:58:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hate my dad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.40,0:59:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad always looks at me with such disgust.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.04,0:59:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see….
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.84,0:59:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That sucks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.91,0:59:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.84,0:59:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.73,0:59:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada-kun your condition is a mental illness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.50,0:59:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So… I think people who talk badly about you are awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.24,0:59:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty awful too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.84,0:59:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.08,0:59:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean by illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.00,0:59:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you understand!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.70,1:00:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.66,1:00:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About the upcoming business trip. Let me go after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.80,1:00:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But your daughter….
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.61,1:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked my mother to take care of her school event.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.51,1:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.28,1:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But… I already asked Hirooka-san.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.50,1:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.15,1:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah okay. I'll go then.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.40,1:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… but….
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.54,1:00:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.62,1:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have kids, so we're more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.69,1:00:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your daughter's school play.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.13,1:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah….}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.07,1:00:37.49,Sign,,0,0,0,,Work's over. What are you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.14,1:00:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{🖩(Message notification sound)}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.59,1:00:56.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.32,1:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“Please, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.92,1:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Duke. Please, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.59,1:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know, what kind of power has emboldened me like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.47,1:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, to express my thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.20,1:01:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,before everyone here
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.60,1:01:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,might be…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.10,1:01:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,against a maiden's modesty maybe…”.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.06,1:01:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of a door opening}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.87,1:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.81,1:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.19,1:01:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.59,1:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.58,1:01:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.48,1:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.95,1:01:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.77,1:01:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.00,1:01:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-zu-ki….
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.84,1:01:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"But, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.15,1:01:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Duke, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.85,1:01:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I refuse to marry Demetrius,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.15,1:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what grave punishment shall I receive?"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of door opening and closing}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.81,1:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.42,1:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.62,1:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.68,1:02:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.92,1:02:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.93,1:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.37,1:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.27,1:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after coming back from cram school she said she wasn't hungry
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.94,1:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and went straight to her room without eating dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.07,1:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.81,1:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey why don't you check on her?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.92,1:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.28,1:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll come down when she's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.38,1:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But she came home an hour later than usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.62,1:02:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was playing with friends?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.58,1:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.40,1:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're her mother, you should….
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.81,1:02:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, she'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.60,1:02:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you….
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.30,1:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just… tired from work.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.64,1:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the….
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.27,1:03:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're tired, does that mean you can just neglect your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.47,1:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not neglecting her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.43,1:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.16,1:03:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As a mother, it's only natural to worry about your daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.76,1:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I'm a mother, it's "natural"…?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.79,1:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't handle being relied on so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.80,1:03:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she relies on you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.93,1:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If a child can't rely on their parents, who else can they rely on?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.30,1:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The times are different from when you were a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.61,1:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, having a place to live was normal, having a family was normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.48,1:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Food is just there, as if it's the most normal thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.51,1:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Being told to be a mother as if it's a given.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.32,1:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Worrying about your daughter has nothing to do with the times, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.59,1:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then mom,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.06,1:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you worried about dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.43,1:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.48,1:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.13,1:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And at your age, you still want to be on stage?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.22,1:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that failing as a wife?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.30,1:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I do take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.20,1:04:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.07,1:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I go to the hospital as much as I can and do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.74,1:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing what I can too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.08,1:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.97,1:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki has no father.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.59,1:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying that now?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.26,1:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if she doesn't have a father?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.03,1:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.50,1:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be both a mother
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.52,1:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and a father.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.60,1:04:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be a single parent, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.51,1:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.98,1:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.18,1:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose it because I thought it was the best!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.61,1:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take proper responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.12,1:04:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am taking responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.32,1:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really such a bad mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.29,1:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.32,1:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that, but….
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.41,1:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so bad to make something in the microwave?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.10,1:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than work do I have to be with my child all the time?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.57,1:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not allowed to think about anything but my child?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.24,1:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.01,1:05:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be a perfect parent….
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.75,1:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No….
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.68,1:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Footsteps}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.26,1:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.93,1:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom I thought you came home. So I just came downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.10,1:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.88,1:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.97,1:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you finish your homework?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.47,1:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.84,1:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.61,1:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.87,1:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh… Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.10,1:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get something ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.95,1:05:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you should eat with us too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.42,1:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.03,1:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.56,1:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.73,1:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This minced meat cutlet is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.87,1:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.07,1:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma how's your practice going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.74,1:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's struggling to memorize their lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.58,1:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only two weeks left so we have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.50,1:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.92,1:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.37,1:06:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your school play practice going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.47,1:06:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah well….
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.26,1:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.74,1:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is practice not going well?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.14,1:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not that…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.78,1:06:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy sitting next to me told me not to act like I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.11,1:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.99,1:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the one who understood him the most.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.36,1:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.28,1:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,people's feelings are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.90,1:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the school play.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.57,1:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.73,1:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom aren't you working?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.58,1:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.88,1:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.57,1:07:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.64,1:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.08,1:07:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.39,1:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.82,1:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,people's feelings are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.97,1:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.26,1:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.32,1:07:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a similar experience like Mizuki did.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.15,1:08:13.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 6th Month (June 1966)
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.41,1:08:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.59,1:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a transfer student named Abe-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.22,1:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Reduce 12/8 to a simple fraction by using common factors.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.73,1:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.26,1:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun, Nishino-san, Tsuda-kun,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.04,1:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,come to the front and give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.11,1:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.39,1:08:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,let me see your homework.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.38,1:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no… I don't want to….
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.60,1:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?! Just show me!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.75,1:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah….
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.72,1:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.98,1:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okajima-san!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.77,1:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Abe-kun's family is definitely poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.47,1:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.47,1:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But but his hands are all dirty and his clothes are super filthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.87,1:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides Abe-kun is bad at studying
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.04,1:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and he picks his nose….
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.64,1:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey stop it already. I'm preparing dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.24,1:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh… I hate sitting next to him. I wish summer break would come so we can change seats.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.89,1:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.13,1:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickle time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.15,1:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time. One more time. {Maybe, this is what was in the subs, not sure}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.65,1:09:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.35,1:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun's shirt
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.06,1:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that was Tanaka-kun's shirt in 4th grade.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.13,1:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.93,1:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.74,1:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun when he's on duck duty
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.48,1:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he takes the duck feed bread home with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.38,1:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.81,1:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.72,1:09:46.33,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.33,1:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.52,1:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is a total secret okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.96,1:09:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.29,1:09:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.80,1:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.29,1:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I dumped the water for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.58,1:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait I was on duck duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.99,1:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The spot Abe-kun touched
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.58,1:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta wipe it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.20,1:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew….
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.96,1:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Abe-kun is taking home the duck bread again today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.63,1:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.86,1:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.14,1:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to family circumstances
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.21,1:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun is transferring schools suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.44,1:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Murmurs}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.98,1:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.69,1:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.82,1:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have everyone shake hands one by one to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.39,1:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh….
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.77,1:11:03.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun let's start from over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.13,1:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not shaking hands with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.14,1:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe-kun knew about it….
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.79,1:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.13,1:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't do something so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.73,1:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch….
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.56,1:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.76,1:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In our class,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.48,1:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anyone else…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.49,1:12:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who hated Abe-kun the most
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.41,1:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was me….
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.72,1:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.28,1:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a bath first.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.91,1:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.57,1:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.30,1:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,About earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.79,1:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.60,1:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.44,1:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.85,1:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.49,1:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.24,1:13:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.52,1:13:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about it made me feel a bit better….
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.59,1:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to your play too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.78,1:13:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.00,1:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.11,1:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.25,1:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But in return, don't embarrass us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.83,1:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate my acting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.94,1:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Laughter}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.75,1:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please Duke
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.73,1:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.79,1:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of power has made me so bold, I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.13,1:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Again to speak my thoughts before everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.94,1:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,may be against a maiden's modesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.70,1:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But please Duke.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.19,1:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.15,1:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I refuse to marry Demetrius what will be
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.95,1:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the severe punishment
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.82,1:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will receive?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.26,1:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause and cheers}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.74,1:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then uh, next
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.65,1:14:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto and Sawada's scene let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.57,1:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.20,1:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.47,1:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.43,1:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.35,1:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.20,1:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.66,1:15:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that kid?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.48,1:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.73,1:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.91,1:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.91,1:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{Applause}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.85,1:15:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing I think you have improved. Really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.92,1:15:26.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,OK\N\NWork's over. What are you doing today?\N\NSorry, I have plans\N\NWe haven't talked much lately, have we?\NWas what I said last time too heavy? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.42,1:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.80,1:15:35.93,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hide - Delete
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.71,1:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.42,1:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Achaa!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.27,1:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.67,1:15:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.57,1:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.65,1:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.04,1:15:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.95,1:15:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stick it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.74,1:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is good?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.82,1:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.05,1:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Diagonally?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.65,1:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilt it a little?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.14,1:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One patch of grass is enough for two pillows.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.50,1:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One heart. One bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.21,1:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Two chests, but one true love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.74,1:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No Lysander.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.77,1:16:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.76,1:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Eek!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.61,1:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermia it's fine just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.38,1:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lysander please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.25,1:16:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come so close move farther away…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.58,1:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No no…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.25,1:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.50,1:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lysander one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.83,1:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh….}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.09,1:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermia it's fine just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.73,1:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.76,1:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time! One more time! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.57,1:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.17,1:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, I haven't seen you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.35,1:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you gotten taller?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.53,1:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.40,1:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{(Computer・Masanobu)「Hmm.}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.61,1:16:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just talked with the doctor…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.18,1:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They said I'll be discharged soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.04,1:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.98,1:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.97,1:16:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.61,1:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With this I can finally see Mom's big moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.88,1:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.78,1:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The play?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.91,1:17:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to watch it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.39,1:17:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that you're still recovering.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.77,1:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.76,1:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to move a bit to regain my strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.36,1:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.75,1:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is looking forward to seeing the great actress perform.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.23,1:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hehehe….}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.79,1:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey who exactly is this great actress?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.29,1:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I meet her?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.82,1:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right in front of you. Look right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.37,1:17:25.03,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where, where? Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.28,1:17:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I'm going to be late for practice!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.91,1:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to be chatting nonsense with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.74,1:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So mean!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.63,1:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright I'm heading off first. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.12,1:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.48,1:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.02,1:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.39,1:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma seems to be having fun every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.83,1:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.92,1:17:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.77,1:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to rehearsal for the school play.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.38,1:17:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey once you're discharged again,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.41,1:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,can we eat Grandpa's food too?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.94,1:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.84,1:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make plenty for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.80,1:17:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.61,1:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late….
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.58,1:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{sobbing}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.88,1:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.28,1:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone pass away?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.55,1:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taeko-san don't say such ominous things!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.69,1:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're crying….
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.49,1:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The performance is getting canceled.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.89,1:18:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.77,1:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.56,1:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The theater we rented
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.16,1:18:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,went bankrupt….
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.65,1:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.34,1:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night we got a call from the theater's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.71,1:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No way… But suddenly telling us now….
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.12,1:18:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I'm just as shocked.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.77,1:18:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning we went to the theater too,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.96,1:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was completely deserted.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.76,1:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there nothing we can do anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.69,1:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we've paid the rental fee, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.93,1:18:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.09,1:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in full, but….
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.40,1:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Partially
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.95,1:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the impact of COVID played a role too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.70,1:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, at this point….
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.06,1:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no….
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.76,1:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.95,1:20:06.66,Sign,,0,0,0,,41st year of the Showa era, 10th Month (October 1966)
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.66,1:20:09.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hyokkori hyotan-jima
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.27,1:20:12.61,Song,,0,0,0,,"The waves go splash splash splash Pushing through the waves.”
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.61,1:20:14.54,Song,,0,0,0,,“Splash Splash Splash”
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.54,1:20:17.78,Song,,0,0,0,,“Swiftly passing through the clouds.”
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.78,1:20:19.85,Song,,0,0,0,,“Swish Swish Swish”
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.75,1:20:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{dunno not in subs}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.68,1:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of a door opening}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.93,1:20:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.95,1:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.74,1:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ito from Nishi University's drama club.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.30,1:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean Taeko?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.31,1:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We'd love to have her join us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.97,1:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.67,1:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We need an actor for a play. We were hoping Taeko could take the role…. {dunno why this line is so long, had to cut it down quite a bit}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.14,1:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd really love for her to participate. Would she be willing to join?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.04,1:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.83,1:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you guys talking about? Was it about a play?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.32,1:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Some university drama club members want Taeko to act in their play.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.52,1:21:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taeko really shined in the school play."
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.54,1:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And? And?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.96,1:21:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They bowed their heads and asked me to let you join.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.40,1:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.87,1:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Taeko.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.27,1:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hehe~.”}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.19,1:21:23.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,Arifune Transport Minister Replaced
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.94,1:21:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really think it's amazing. To be offered such an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.11,1:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess everyone has at least one talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.42,1:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Taeko is good at writing, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.81,1:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Taeko has more talent in that than in math.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.12,1:21:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really really?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.96,1:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I played the old man in "Tongue-Cut Sparrow", but
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.63,1:21:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got any offers.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.30,1:21:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.80,1:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.90,1:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.84,1:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:22:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be the start of a career as a child actress.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.95,1:22:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you should join Takarazuka!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.12,1:22:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.16,1:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start training now, you might get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.89,1:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! Really? Eek!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.25,1:22:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.70,1:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.46,1:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh….}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.93,1:22:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Show business is out of the question. {was entertainment industry but had to shorten it}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.84,1:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on… 'show business' is an overstatement.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.27,1:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But still….
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.41,1:22:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.74,1:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.42,1:22:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes….
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.95,1:22:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a shy and
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.27,1:22:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,introverted girl….
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.62,1:22:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.63,1:22:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.01,1:22:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.45,1:22:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.50,1:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of door opening/closing}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.91,1:23:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sobbing}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.22,1:23:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do it… I really wanted to do it….
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.77,1:23:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do it….
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.95,1:23:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.29,1:23:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sigh… Hmm….}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.79,1:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sound of door opening}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.35,1:23:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.30,1:23:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.26,1:23:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah wash my hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.57,1:24:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.48,1:24:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.32,1:24:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.31,1:24:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's practice with everyone was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.15,1:24:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I understood something.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.19,1:24:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.26,1:24:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like our feelings became one.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.04,1:24:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, I never felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.28,1:24:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But today I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.60,1:24:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.54,1:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone cherished each and every moment!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.77,1:24:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And then somehow I felt like we were all connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.48,1:24:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.12,1:24:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.95,1:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.88,1:24:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Living on stage is what matters
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.50,1:24:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.62,1:24:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I did!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.20,1:24:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And today I finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.95,1:24:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.03,1:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.30,1:25:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Grandma too
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.85,1:25:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,has been training all this time
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.41,1:25:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And once again I realized how important that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.42,1:25:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.93,1:25:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.74,1:25:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.68,1:25:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.78,1:25:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.39,1:25:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.58,1:25:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up. Not over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.19,1:25:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can give up now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.29,1:25:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.75,1:25:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you. For telling me!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.39,1:25:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.82,1:25:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.27,1:25:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mmm! Yeah}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.17,1:25:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.91,1:25:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.12,1:26:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Still Mom was so unlucky. Shakespeare. {seems wrong}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.89,1:26:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.93,1:26:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Life goes on. There are many things in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.73,1:26:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To live is to face trials.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.57,1:26:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Mom's dream didn't come true,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.78,1:26:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least you get to see your grandchild's play.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.34,1:26:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that happiness?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.56,1:26:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.79,1:26:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I gave up?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.59,1:26:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.70,1:26:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But the play got canceled….
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.25,1:26:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.07,1:26:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just canceled this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.51,1:26:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.19,1:26:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I took another audition.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.76,1:26:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.52,1:26:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...And I passed!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.89,1:26:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.26,1:26:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Chekhov. Amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.93,1:26:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable….
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.83,1:26:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.60,1:26:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.84,1:26:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.11,1:26:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey stop it. She only has one line.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.78,1:27:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherish every moment!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.05,1:27:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.99,1:27:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah yeah! Hehehe}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.92,1:27:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.24,1:28:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{♬}
